Description:
    Jekyll post generator. Give it a title name, and an optional list of
    categories.

Example:
    yeoman init jekyll:post Post title

    This will create:
        _posts/2012-10-14-post-title.md

    yeoman init jekyll:post "About me" --category blog --category bio

    This will create:
        _posts/2012-10-14-about-me.md (but with `categories: [blog, bio]` in the YAML front matter)

    yeoman init jekyll:post Stuff

